docs.title: About Me
docs.text: Accomplished Data Engineer with 3 years of experience in the financial and healthcare industries, known for innovative solutions and a positive outlook. Expertise in Python, SQL, Azure, Google Cloud, and data processing. Master's in Data Science from the University of Glasgow. Passionate about public speaking and promoting eurodiversity in tech.
